# Link Checker Exclusions
# Domains and patterns to exclude from link checking to avoid false positives

# Social media sharing/redirect URLs (not content links)
# These redirect to login pages or are rate-limited
https://twitter.com/intent/tweet*
https://twitter.com/share*
https://x.com/intent/tweet*
https://x.com/share*
https://t.co/*
https://www.facebook.com/sharer/*
facebook.com/sharer/*
https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle*
linkedin.com/shareArticle*
https://pinterest.com/pin/create/*
pinterest.com/pin/create/*
https://www.instagram.com/share*
whatsapp://send*

# Social media profile URLs
# Instagram aggressively rate-limits and blocks automated checkers
https://instagram.com/*
https://www.instagram.com/*
# LinkedIn profiles often require authentication
https://linkedin.com/in/*
https://www.linkedin.com/in/*
https://linkedin.com/company/*
https://www.linkedin.com/company/*

# CDNs and external resources
https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/*
https://unpkg.com/*
https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/*

# Analytics and tracking
https://www.google-analytics.com/*
https://analytics.google.com/*

# Comment systems
https://disqus.com/*

# Localhost and development
http://localhost*
http://127.0.0.1*

# Mail links
mailto:*
